message.body: Now i am! Kinda. So sleepy, my love. So sleepy. How are you, darling?
I'm so sorry my love! I thought I had responded, but I never pressed send! I called you, but no answer. I hope you're feeling better. I love you!!!
I want chicken biryani...can you help me with that when youre down here? :) Thats basically where my sleep deprived mind is at right now. And i love you. A lot.
Hahahaha. YES! Chicken biryani. I want it too! Let's do it. And I love you too. Get some sleep now!
Woohoo!! I'll find the bestest indian food in town before you get here haha. And no sleep! Lots to do!! You promise to have a good day :)
Only if you do! Gots lots of studying to do. Awful.
Ewww...but, im planning to have an excellent day...and i'll send good vibes your way and lotta lotta mushy love and luck and such.
Oh. That sounds like a plan to me!!! Definitely!
Haha good luck, my love! Dont go too crazy please please.
I'm not going to go crazy. IM GOING TO GO iNSANE! Heh. Jk. Ill be okay.
Ahah daaaarling, you betta not!! I like yo mind. No going nutso haha
